nodes.text: Ulendale was a destination on the Coruscant train. It appeared on a list of stops that popped up on a data screen at the train station where Ahsoka Tano and Tera Sinube tracked Ione Marcy and Cassie Cryar. Also listed was Burbank, Arabia and Alderaan. For reasons unknown, the same data screens were also found in Tipoca City on Kamino.
